Package: ctdnaTM
Type: Package
Title: ctDNA Deliverables
Version: 0.75.10
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Hamid", family = "Nikbakht",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "hamid.nikbakht@noreply.github.com")
  )
Description: Standardised plotting, statistics, and multi-modal integration
    helpers for the core ctDNA deliverables built around the
    Guardant Health Infinity platform but extensible to other vendors.
    Every plot function exposes a `stat` parameter with a recommended
    default per the pipeline conventions, surfaced as RStudio Tab tooltips.
